ANALYSIS OF LIDAR APPLICATIONS AND HARDWARE  
(Name)  
(Date)

This engineering analysis evaluates the various resources documented for generating and importing 3D assets into Unity, focusing on technical capabilities, optimization potential, cost, and workflow efficiency.1. 3D Scanning Applications (Asset Generation)

The mobile applications reviewed are primarily used for generating 3D meshes from real-world objects using LiDAR or photogrammetry. The key difference among them for an engineering pipeline is the accessibility of export formats (FBX, OBJ, STL) and processing speed.

