**Assessment of Scanning Tools:**

For a free, unconstrained pipeline, **Scaniverse** is the most viable option due to its free use of Unity-compatible export formats and faster, offline processing. **PolyCam** offers higher-end features and larger capture limits (up to 2000 images in Pro), but these require a significant subscription fee to access standard formats like FBX. RealityScan is free but relies on complex cloud processing for detail.2. Pipeline Optimization Tools (Data Preparation for Unity)[1](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1HNeGzajTROzYAehrWHzndxrEasepNs7gf_7EesUlaz4/edit)

Optimizing 3D models—especially large CAD files—is critical for real-time engine performance in Unity.

